
- Requirements:

  - A C++ compiler with C++14 support.
    The following compilers have been tested:
    - GCC 5.4 (Linux+GNU x86_64).
    - GCC 7.1 (Linux+GNU x86_64).

  - Qt 5 (tested with version 5.7.1).

  - JACK Audio Connection Kit (tested with version 1.9.10).

  - FFTW - single precision (tested with version 3.3.4).

  - GamaTTS (use the latest version).
    For local install, the source must be in ../gama_tts and the build directory
    must be ../gama_tts-build.

- Local install:

  qmake
  make

  - Start the JACK server using QjackCtl.

  # Test.
  LD_LIBRARY_PATH=../gama_tts-build ./gama_tts_editor

- System install:

  qmake
  make
  make install
  #make install INSTALL_ROOT=/tmp/install

  - Start the JACK server using QjackCtl.

  # Test.
  gama_tts_editor

- Note:

  - The sampling rate in JACK must be equal to the value of the parameter
    "output_rate" in the file vtm.config (default: 44100).
